title: Wordpress plugin - Codecanyon DVin WooCommerce Wishlist - 03.04.
description:
The WooCommerce Wishlist Plugin for WordPress allows your visitors/customers to add products to a personal wishlist that they may save to purchase later or share with their friends. Increase your conversion rates by allowing your customers to maintain a list of products they would like to buy. Increase the usefulness by allowing them to share it on tools they are familiar with: Email, Facebook, Twitter, and Pinterest.

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
